@startuml
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor #F7FCFF
    BorderColor #88BBDD
    FontSize 12
}

note over App, VFS
mount 挂载核心流程（super_operations）
1. 解析设备、挂载点、文件系统类型
2. 分配并初始化超级块 super_block
3. 调用 s_op->read_inode 读取 root inode
4. 创建挂载点 dentry 与根目录关联
5. 建立文件系统层级挂载关系
end note

box "【用户态 User Space】" #LightYellow
actor App
end box

box "【内核态 Kernel Space】" #LightCyan
participant "VFS 虚拟文件系统" as VFS
participant "super_block" as SB
participant "root_inode" as RootInode
participant "挂载点 dentry" as MountPoint
end box

database "磁盘/分区" as Disk

' ========== 流程开始 ============
App -> VFS: <color:red>①</color> mount("/dev/sdb1", "/mnt", "ext4")
activate VFS

VFS -> VFS: <color:red>②</color> 查找文件系统类型（ext4）
VFS -> SB: <color:red>③</color> 分配 super_block 结构体
activate SB

VFS -> SB: <color:red>④</color> 调用 sb->s_op->fill_super()
note right: 读取磁盘超级块、初始化 super_operations
SB --> VFS: 超级块初始化完成

VFS -> RootInode: <color:red>⑤</color> 读取根目录 inode(ino=1)
activate RootInode
RootInode --> VFS: 返回 root inode & root dentry
deactivate RootInode

VFS -> MountPoint: <color:red>⑥</color> 绑定挂载点 /mnt
activate MountPoint
MountPoint --> VFS: 挂载点 dentry 关联新文件系统
deactivate MountPoint

VFS -> VFS: <color:red>⑦</color> 加入全局挂载链表
VFS --> App: <color:red>⑧</color> 挂载成功返回0
deactivate SB
deactivate VFS
@enduml